reviewText: I really only wanted Diggstown and this was the cheapest way to buy it.  The other movies were a huge plus but most of them I have seen too many times.
This was purchased as a christmas gift for my husband. Excellent value for money My darling husband  isvery happy with it.
This was a gift for my son and he loves it. It cost less just the one movie he wanted but he likes all the movies.
Bought this movie for Diggstown, can't beat the price compared to the cost of buying it separately and you get other great movies.  I look forward to watching them all.

shipping was pretty fast only 8 days, including order date. great price for 6 movies, i just bought it for diggstown, & this set was cheaper than just diggstown on it's own. good price & good shipping = good buy!
